to start a project: 
-- composer global require laravel/installer
-- laravel new laragigproject
-- cd laragigproject
-- php artisan serve

<!-- =========ROUTING============ -->
- We change our routing  inside the routes folder
- the specific file is web.php
- to use blade, we must give the file a name filename.blade.php
- inside web.php, under route, view, we only specify the name of the file. we dont add blade.php. 
- 
<!-- use of directives -->
- directives start with @ symbol. 
- used instead of having php tags all over

<!-- MODELS  -->
- Models are found inside app folder